title: Bobby Gets Personal With Dr. Oz + Raymundo’s Financial Rules + Mike D Sets A Wedding Date

description:
We talk to Dr. Oz who answers all of our health questions including one Bobby had about bottled water and having kids. Raymundo tells us about a rule he and his wife have implemented just two weeks into their marriage. Plus, Mike D has set a wedding date!
